To use Git and Github
1 from the team menu of a project choose share project
2 Choose GIT
3 Create the repository in the folder
4 Commit to the repository

To Add to git hub
1 from the Git view choose the repository 
2 choose push the repository
3 Supply the http of the git repository 
4 pick select "add all branchs spec" button 

To import a github
1 use import
2 projects from git
3 uri
4 add https of project
5 select where you want the code
6 say ok to everything